{"talk":{"id":27750,"name":"Dawn Wacek: A librarian's case against overdue book fines","description":"Libraries have the power to create a better world; they connect communities, promote literacy and spark lifelong learners. But there's one thing that keeps people away: the fear of overdue book fines. In this thought-provoking talk, librarian Dawn Wacek makes the case that fines don't actually do what we think they do. What if your library just ... stopped asking for them altogether?","slug":"dawn_wacek_a_librarian_s_case_against_overdue_book_fines","recorded_at":"2018-02-08 00:00:00","published_at":"2018-11-15 15:51:38","updated_at":"2021-04-09 19:46:19","viewed_count":1321018,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":567,"name":"TEDxUWLaCrosse"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/6c908a8532ecac3c4959a8dc486adae4a9e6c92d_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/6c908a8532ecac3c4959a8dc486adae4a9e6c92d_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/6c908a8532ecac3c4959a8dc486adae4a9e6c92d_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/6c908a8532ecac3c4959a8dc486adae4a9e6c92d_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/cd4b28e74ead7769db2414ccad21176e9051e778_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/DawnWacek_2018X-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":6859651,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/DawnWacek_2018X-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":19010859,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/DawnWacek_2018X-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":33628520,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"450k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/DawnWacek_2018X-450k.mp